                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
                    黃頜蛇科，<a class="site-link" href="http://www.probertencyclopaedia.com/B_PAREINAE.HTM">亞洲食蝸蛇亞科</a>
                    <br>
                    <span lang="en-US">Colubridae, subfamily <a class="site-link" href="http://www.probertencyclopaedia.com/B_PAREINAE.HTM">Pareatinae</a></span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
